**[Question #16]{.underline}**: Will I get additional breaks on the
12-hour shifts?

**[Answer #16:]{.underline}** Yes. All 12-hour shifts will have four
15-minute paid rest periods in addition to a 20-minute paid lunch.

**[Question #17]{.underline}**: What about Bereavement Leave?

**[Answer #17:]{.underline}** You will be allowed the same number of
paid days off on a 24/7 schedule as you are currently allowed on the
traditional schedule.

**[Question #16:]{.underline}** How will shift differentials be paid on
the 12-hour schedule?

**[Answer #16:]{.underline}** On the 12-hour schedule, employees on the
24/7 Night Shift schedule will receive a shift differential of
\$.50/hour for all 12 hours

